FT  24 FEB 93 / UK Company News: Shirescot
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Shires High-Yielding Smaller Companies Trust reported a net asset value of
111.5p per share as at December 31; fully diluted the figure was 109.58p.
The trust, launched on August 28, achieved net revenue of Pounds 334,000 for
